I guess you mean Phobia instead of Zardus?

Phobia looked at Hysteria, he was surprised that it was her doing the work.

"Ah hello again my friend, I suppose that it takes a delicate Bot to
administer a delicate touch."Phobias two faced charm was so sweet it could
give cavities to the tooth fairy.

"I have here all the maintenance parts from a Predacon warship, if they're
compatible with your systems Kluster can lead the victory over the Iron
Fist." Like a polatician near voting dayPhobia manipulates his words with
master skill. His eyes don't move off his target audience, his voice doesn't
quiver, he sound as sure of this plan like it's already a done task.
